ta-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3613872\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jdo1665702650723.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jdo1665702650723.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jdo1665702650723.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jdo1665702650723\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Alignment or Text Position (align)\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This property determines whether the labels (that is, the representation of a ValRep value) for radio group buttons appear to the <code class=\"ph codeph\">Left</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">Right</code> (default) of the buttons.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jdo1665702650723__section_w3422ab1b5b1_w3423ab1b5_w3424ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"jdo1665702650723__table_d11516e1_d11517e1_d11518e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jdo1665702650723__table_d11516e1_d11517e1_d11518e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jdo1665702650723__table_d11516e1_d11517e1_d11518e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jdo1665702650723__table_d11516e1_d11517e1_d11518e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">(default)</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jdo1665702650723__table_d11516e1_d11517e1_d11518e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The default.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jdo1665702650723__table_d11516e1_d11517e1_d11518e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Left</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jdo1665702650723__table_d11516e1_d11517e1_d11518e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The representations appear to the left of the radio buttons.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jdo1665702650723__table_d11516e1_d11517e1_d11518e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Right</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jdo1665702650723__table_d11516e1_d11517e1_d11518e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The representations appear to the right of the radio buttons.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jdo1665702650723__section_blh_1jf_rwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d714929e142\">Limitations</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jdo1665702650723__p_d99311e1_d99312e1_d99313e1\">If the representations are left-aligned, a 3D effect\n            cannot be applied to the radio buttons.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jdo1665702650723__section_clj_bjf_rwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d714929e151\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"jdo1665702650723__ul_smn_djf_rwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jdo1665702650723__li_d40007e1_d40008e1_d40009e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yye1665702650577.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yye1665702650577.html\" title=\"The uradiogroup widget displays a set of mutually exclusive choices as a group of radio buttons. Uniface provides a logical widget called RadioGroup, which is mapped to uradiogroup.\">uradiogroup (RadioGroup)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613872\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613872\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Alignment or Text Position (align) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Alignment or Text Position (align) This property determines whether the labels (that is, the representation of a ValRep value) for radio group buttons appear to the Left or Right (default) of the buttons. Value Description (default) The default. Left The representations appear to the left of the radio buttons. Right The representations appear to the right of the radio buttons. Limitations If the representations are left-aligned, a 3D effect cannot be applied to the radio buttons. Applies To uradiogroup (RadioGroup) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}